column7: PROBLEM: CORNING HAS QTY 3 SVW250 IN THEIR POSSESSION:(SVW2502595, SVW2502596, SVW2503399). THEY REQUIRE A NEW SYSTEM TO HAVE THE SAME CONFIGURATION WITH A WHITE BACKLIGHT LED. THE CURRENT SVW250 MACHINES HAVE A BACKLIGHT THAT IS GREEN.  ROOT CAUSE: WHEN BACKLIGHT ASSEMBLY 529580 LED WAS CHANGED FROM, WHITE TO GREEN ON ECN 22249 IT WAS NO LONGER BACKWARDS COMPATIBLE. A NEW PART NUMBER SHOULD HAVE BEEN REQUESTED.  SOLUTION: RELEASE 529580-2 WITH ORIGINAL WHITE LED FOR DUPLICATE MACHINE ORDERS.
